divs: Sighting DetailsWas taking pictures one afternoon of my aquarium. Nothing out of the ordinary until a few months later I uploaded them on my computer to sort through them and pick the best ones I took. I noticed only 1 image had something unusual in it. Apparently at the time of taking these photos I think and I don't know how there was an alien gray behind me.
